race.description: De Bortoli Wines Country Boosted Handicap (Bm58)
race.comment: OUR EMILY (4) scored first up two runs ago but couldn't back it up last time. Fitter and deserves another chance. DUBALENE (9) is resuming and having her first run for the Colt Prosser yard. Was in the placings when first-up from a spell last campaign. Placed in a recent trial and makes plenty of appeal in the new surrounds. TOOMUCHINFORMATION (2) also resumes. Doesn't win out of turn but has efforts littered through his form that can measure up. Also worth noting his solid record at this venue. SHINE YOUR LIGHT (5) was in the money two starts back at Armidale but was unable to repeat the effort last time. Finds a nice race and can make amends.
